item.title: New rsps
item.dc:creator: @OGolemX OGolemX
item.description:
@OGolemX wrote:

  1. Sexybawz-scape.
  2. Staff of light.
  3. Whydontyouhostityourself
    4 & 5. Go through all server files and press (ctrl + h) and a search bar will open, in the first bar search the old server name then in the second typing bar, type the new rsps name, and then click on (Replace All). Do that within all files with the old server name in them.
